longBusinessSummary: Indo Farm Equipment Limited manufactures and sells agricultural, industrial, and construction equipment in India. It offers tractors, rotary tillers, harvesters, and other related spares and components; and hydraulic pick and carry cranes, and mobile tower cranes. The company also engages in asset financing business with a focus on retail financing of tractors. It exports its products to Europe, Asia, North and South Africa, and other countries in Asia. The company was formerly known as Indo Farm Industries Limited and changed its name to Indo Farm Equipment Limited in November 2009. Indo Farm Equipment Limited was incorporated in 1994 and is based in Baddi, India.
